/ 
/================================================================================
/ PARAMETERS:
/-------name------- -------------------------description-------------------------
/ autolib           (pos) Name of the macro library to concatenate. This should
/                   be unquoted if it is a fileref or quoted if a path name.
/ pos               (pos - unquoted) Position in the list. Can be first or last
/                   or front or back.
